name: avril15 - Consciousness Is a Hell of a Drug

metadata.name: Consciousness Is a Hell of a Drug by avril15
metadata.description:
- no time, no place  
- memories but fractionalized, framed and distorted.  
- a lone eyeball, a doorway and an entrance to the night sky.  
- a goddess but not as we remember her.  
- nostalgia, of course, but trapped in a window...
